es into the template context under the key . This allows us to easily loop over and display these similar movies in the template.Finally, we return the updated context dictionary, ensuring that both the primary movie details and its related recommendations (similar movies) are available to our template.Now, we simply need to iterate over the movies array and display it in the template. Go back to the moviematchapp/templates/moviematchapp/movie_detail.html file and add the following code:{% if movies %}
